 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010008811950684

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.066003084182739

===========

 SELECT id,name, image, alias
							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_tai_nghe,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC
							 

time:::0.061004161834717

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%4%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.002000093460083

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.0020010471343994

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special

						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						 WHERE  published = 1 and category_published = 1 
						  ORDER BY   ordering DESC,created_time DESC
						 LIMIT 1

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.0010008811950684

===========

							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_tai_nghe,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC
							 

time:::0.00099992752075195

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

							FROM fs_manufactories

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0

						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%4%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						 LIMIT 1

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.0010008811950684

					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%4%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.002500057220459

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0039999485015869

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.003000020980835

===========

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10
